**Overview**

This dashboard provides information about the Audit events collected by the Microsoft DNS Server integration.

These events track changes and access to the DNS server configuration and records, which are crucial for security auditing purposes. They help in monitoring unauthorized access attempts or modifications to the DNS settings.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/microsoft_dnsserver/overview)
